at last :
cd ~/docker-swarm-vms
vagrant status
vagrant ssh manager-vm
docker node ls
docker service ps java-web-app
http://192.168.56.10:9090

Open a new terminal tab on your laptop (don't close the manager tab).

Stop one of the workers:

cd ~/docker-swarm-vms
vagrant halt worker1-vm

Go back to your manager terminal tab and run:

docker service ps java-web-app

